results.title: Felt fun bandana crown
results.description:
I came by this felt 'crown' from my former exercise instructor.  She gave it to me about ten years ago.  She said she and her friends had made these crowns for a life party many years earlier.  I think she used some much older fabrics and trim and thread at the time. So, it's about 25 years old but it's components are much older.  It is well made with visible double stitching and appliques of a fun moon and star.  She was a very gregarious and fun loving person.  "live, laugh, love!"  is very good advice.  I can see this as the part of any costume for Halloween or play time.  It is pretty firm to the touch and should stay in place.  Quality felt and accented with crystal bead dangles.  No opening.  One size fits all.  

I intend to get this into the mail within 3 business days.  Happy to combine shipping if you see other items you cannot live without.  

Your patronage is greatly appreciated

results.title: Live Laugh Love Heart 3D Printed Valentines Anniversary Love Weddings  Cookie Cutter
results.description:
SIZE

         -Roughly 4 inches across

INSTRUCTIONS FOR USE:

          -Use non-raising dough for the best outcome
          -Use with a dough thickness of 1/5 inch or 5mm
          -Coat dough and Cookie Cutter in flour for each cut so the dough does not stick to the cutter


TIPS:

           -If you run into the issue of getting dough stuck inside the cookie cutter this is from either the dough being to thick or not using enough flour.  To remove the dough from the cutter let it soak in tepid water and use a toothbrush to remove the stuck dough.

INSTRUCTIONS FOR WASHING:

          -Never use hot water or put in the dishwasher
         - Hand wash with tepid soapy water and a toothbrush to remove remnants
